plptool.mips

Class Asm

  • java.lang.Object
    • plptool.PLPAsm
      • plptool.mips.Asm

  • public class Asm
extends PLPAsm
    This class implements the modular PLP assembler object. The default constructor will initialize required symbols for the assembler. The assembler class can handle multiple assembly sources and cross-references.

      • sanitize16bits

        public static long sanitize16bits(java.lang.String number)
                           throws java.lang.Exception
        Take in a string and attempts to parse it as a 16 bit number. This 16-bit number is stored in int primitive (32-bit data type) to preserve all 16-bits of data since Java doesn't have unsigned data types. Higher 2-bytes of the number are masked.
        Parameters:
        Number - to be sanitized in String
        Returns:
        Returns 16-bit number in long with higher 2-bytes masked , returns PLP_NUMBER_ERROR if parseInt failed.
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception
        See Also:
        sanitize32bits(String)

      • sanitize32bits

        public static long sanitize32bits(java.lang.String number)
                           throws java.lang.Exception
        Take in a string and attempts to parse it as a 32 bit number. This 32-bit number is stored in long primitive (64-bit data type) to preserve all 32-bits of data since Java doesn't have unsigned data types. Higher 4-bytes of the number are masked.
        Parameters:
        Number - to be sanitized in String
        Returns:
        Returns 32-bit number in long with higher 4-bytes masked , returns PLP_NUMBER_ERROR if parseLong failed.
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception
        See Also:
        sanitize16bits(String)
